## 📂 Loyihani ishga tushirish

```bash
# Repositoriyani klonlash
git clone https://github.com/username/noutbuk-sayt.git

# Papkaga kirish
cd noutbuk-sayt

# index.html faylini brauzerda ochish
open index.html
```

